1
00:00:18,656 --> 00:00:19,656
Darling

2
00:00:22,118 --> 00:00:23,118
please come back.

3
00:00:24,036 --> 00:00:25,371
A message from Supremo.

4
00:00:28,708 --> 00:00:30,042
I'm sorry, Ace.

5
00:00:30,292 --> 00:00:31,961
I can't come back to you.

6
00:00:33,045 --> 00:00:35,423
Let's late fate decide everything.

7
00:00:37,331 --> 00:00:38,874
You're so fragile

8
00:00:39,552 --> 00:00:41,220
and easy to break, Zein.

9
00:00:43,222 --> 00:00:45,057
Let that monster out.

10
00:00:46,726 --> 00:00:48,102
Let it go, Zein.

11
00:00:49,437 --> 00:00:50,813
Protect yourself.

12
00:00:52,189 --> 00:00:54,859
All classes are suspended.

13
00:00:55,651 --> 00:00:57,862
There will be a meeting
at the conference room.

14
00:00:58,320 --> 00:01:00,740
1:30 pm mandatory.

15
00:01:02,074 --> 00:01:04,952
We have been trying to
complete a formula for years now.

16
00:01:07,246 --> 00:01:10,124
A formula that can bring back the dead.

17
00:01:12,543 --> 00:01:17,006
We're asking for your
cooperation one last time.

18
00:01:19,300 --> 00:01:20,300
Now

19
00:01:20,551 --> 00:01:22,094
all of you must rest.

20
00:01:24,638 --> 00:01:25,638
Darling

21
00:01:26,265 --> 00:01:27,433
please come back.

22
00:01:28,184 --> 00:01:29,184
I will...

23
00:01:31,377 --> 00:01:32,455
No!

24
00:01:33,481 --> 00:01:34,482
Not her!

25
00:01:34,899 --> 00:01:35,899
Stop!

26
00:01:36,358 --> 00:01:37,443
No!

27
00:01:38,778 --> 00:01:39,987
Let her go!

28
00:01:40,529 --> 00:01:41,529
Zein!

29
00:01:41,614 --> 00:01:42,656
Let her go!

30
00:01:47,411 --> 00:01:48,411
Zein!

31
00:01:48,496 --> 00:01:49,496
Zein!

32
00:01:50,539 --> 00:01:51,539
Zein!

33
00:02:14,271 --> 00:02:15,369
Hello secretary

34
00:02:15,981 --> 00:02:16,981
how are you?

35
00:02:57,721 --> 00:02:58,889
Hello, Miss Secretary.

36
00:02:59,757 --> 00:03:00,757
How are you?

37
00:03:03,153 --> 00:03:04,738
I am better than fine.

38
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:08,247
Welcome to our hidden laboratory.

39
00:03:11,787 --> 00:03:12,787
Thanks.

40
00:03:15,437 --> 00:03:16,437
Are we ready?

41
00:03:21,432 --> 00:03:22,559
I'm so sorry.

42
00:03:25,551 --> 00:03:26,551
For what?

43
00:03:28,012 --> 00:03:29,305
Please forgive my mom.

44
00:03:32,366 --> 00:03:34,869
Do you think "sorry" will make up for this?

45
00:03:35,261 --> 00:03:38,055
For all the lives your mother ruined?

46
00:03:40,150 --> 00:03:41,775
A lot of students are dead.

47
00:03:42,985 --> 00:03:44,904
Open your fucking eyes!

48
00:03:46,313 --> 00:03:47,440
To be honest with you.

49
00:03:48,449 --> 00:03:49,950
I'm jealous of you.

50
00:03:53,610 --> 00:03:55,370
The relationship you
have with your friends.

51
00:03:59,541 --> 00:04:05,713
I wish I had that kind of friendship.

52
00:04:06,943 --> 00:04:10,113
You can also have that

53
00:04:12,787 --> 00:04:15,540
just stop living under
your mother’s shadow, Liam.

54
00:04:17,311 --> 00:04:18,520
But I can't.

55
00:04:20,033 --> 00:04:23,947
I have no one else but her.

56
00:04:28,030 --> 00:04:29,031
Liam...

57
00:04:29,907 --> 00:04:30,908
please.

58
00:04:31,951 --> 00:04:33,400
It's not too late.

59
00:04:34,078 --> 00:04:35,204
Please help us.

60
00:04:36,038 --> 00:04:36,729
I...

61
00:04:36,754 --> 00:04:37,289
I can't.

62
00:04:37,331 --> 00:04:38,999
I can't, I'm so sorry. I can't.

63
00:04:40,751 --> 00:04:41,751
Why?

64
00:04:42,044 --> 00:04:44,338
Scared to follow your master's orders?

65
00:04:46,382 --> 00:04:47,716
Prepare her.

66
00:04:49,593 --> 00:04:52,554
You found the last ingredient
for your most precious formula

67
00:04:53,806 --> 00:04:55,391
so please stop this.

68
00:04:56,767 --> 00:04:58,018
Let us go.

69
00:04:58,401 --> 00:04:59,485
Let you go?

70
00:05:00,106 --> 00:05:01,566
What do you think of me? Stupid?

71
00:05:02,566 --> 00:05:04,424
I didn't spend all
these years trying to

72
00:05:04,449 --> 00:05:07,322
find the formula just
to spend it in prison.

73
00:05:10,088 --> 00:05:11,590
No witnesses.

74
00:05:12,167 --> 00:05:13,794
No mistakes.

75
00:05:14,341 --> 00:05:15,551
What are you planning to do?

76
00:05:16,010 --> 00:05:17,511
Kill us all?

77
00:05:18,423 --> 00:05:21,677
Do not underestimate
my will, Ms. Zein Shion.

78
00:05:22,970 --> 00:05:25,013
You won't get away with this.

79
00:05:25,608 --> 00:05:26,608
Oh really?

80
00:05:27,256 --> 00:05:28,507
You should know Ms. Zein

81
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:31,494
I've been very lucky lately.

82
00:05:31,841 --> 00:05:35,470
Two pieces of the puzzle
has landed in my lap.

83
00:05:39,748 --> 00:05:41,375
First, you.

84
00:05:44,090 --> 00:05:45,090
Me?

85
00:05:45,709 --> 00:05:46,960
What are the chances?

86
00:05:46,985 --> 00:05:50,614
Aside from the special treatment
Supremo has been giving you

87
00:05:50,806 --> 00:05:52,646
turns out there's
something special about you.

88
00:05:53,493 --> 00:05:58,373
An exceptionally rare blood type
with an exceptionally rare blood component.

89
00:06:07,875 --> 00:06:09,042
Impossible.

90
00:06:17,467 --> 00:06:21,221
You need my blood for the serum.

91
00:06:21,455 --> 00:06:22,971
You stumbling here

92
00:06:23,502 --> 00:06:25,638
and eventually
enrolling in this university

93
00:06:25,662 --> 00:06:27,798
it the best thing that
ever happened for me.

94
00:06:28,979 --> 00:06:29,980
But of course

95
00:06:30,171 --> 00:06:32,158
extracting your blood was
tricky.

96
00:06:32,569 --> 00:06:36,580
We tried several times to replicate
the process without the formula

97
00:06:36,715 --> 00:06:38,300
and we failed several times.

98
00:06:39,663 --> 00:06:43,959
Dr. Razon is not as smart
as Dr. Quizon apparently.

99
00:06:45,061 --> 00:06:46,061
Shame.

100
00:06:46,478 --> 00:06:47,854
We wanted the formula.

101
00:06:48,342 --> 00:06:51,095
We wanted to give up after all these years.

102
00:06:51,966 --> 00:06:56,595
We thought it would be kept by
the brightest student in this university,

103
00:06:56,968 --> 00:06:58,261
maybe a mathematician

104
00:06:58,451 --> 00:06:59,493
a scientist

105
00:07:00,645 --> 00:07:05,025
but it turns out an artist kept it hidden.

106
00:07:06,065 --> 00:07:08,067
Do you like manga?

107
00:07:16,094 --> 00:07:17,094
Celine...

108
00:07:18,288 --> 00:07:19,664
You killed Celine?

109
00:07:19,917 --> 00:07:20,917
I'm sorry

110
00:07:21,123 --> 00:07:22,123
is that her name?

111
00:07:22,754 --> 00:07:24,755
Sorry if I can't remember
the names of the students

112
00:07:24,780 --> 00:07:27,283
here in this godforsaken university.

113
00:07:28,992 --> 00:07:31,202
She wasn't an ordinary student.

114
00:07:32,425 --> 00:07:33,718
She was smart

115
00:07:34,403 --> 00:07:35,404
and talented.

116
00:07:36,497 --> 00:07:38,207
And you will remember her name.

117
00:07:38,690 --> 00:07:41,860
You will remember all of the names of
the students you've killed!

118
00:07:43,123 --> 00:07:45,334
And what are you going to do about it?

119
00:07:45,529 --> 00:07:46,529
Huh?

120
00:07:48,396 --> 00:07:50,148
Supremo will come for me.

121
00:07:51,481 --> 00:07:52,941
You don't know him like I do.

122
00:07:53,835 --> 00:07:55,086
He's coming.

123
00:07:57,007 --> 00:07:59,217
I highly doubt.

124
00:08:06,748 --> 00:08:08,959
Let's proceed with the extraction.

125
00:08:12,971 --> 00:08:13,971
No!

126
00:08:14,293 --> 00:08:15,419
Stop!

127
00:08:15,971 --> 00:08:17,138
No!

128
00:08:18,641 --> 00:08:19,641
No!

129
00:08:24,516 --> 00:08:25,726
Don't touch me.

130
00:08:26,727 --> 00:08:28,437
Let me go!

131
00:08:29,271 --> 00:08:30,439
Stop!

132
00:08:30,464 --> 00:08:31,464
No!

133
00:10:01,796 --> 00:10:02,797
Stop!

134
00:10:03,365 --> 00:10:04,366
No!

135
00:10:04,982 --> 00:10:06,317
No!

136
00:10:07,275 --> 00:10:08,275
Let me go!

137
00:10:09,635 --> 00:10:10,635
Stop it!

138
00:10:40,464 --> 00:10:42,091
Compatibility optimal.

139
00:11:17,773 --> 00:11:18,773
Where's Zein?

140
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:20,676
Underground.

141
00:11:20,982 --> 00:11:22,024
In the lab.

142
00:11:23,884 --> 00:11:25,594
They're preparing her for extraction.

143
00:11:26,302 --> 00:11:28,470
Violet's finally going
to get what she wants.

144
00:11:29,923 --> 00:11:32,050
Our time in hell is almost over.

145
00:11:32,790 --> 00:11:34,209
This is wrong, Ms. Kath.

146
00:11:36,023 --> 00:11:37,233
You're not like them.

147
00:11:38,011 --> 00:11:39,513
We need to stop Violet.

148
00:11:41,034 --> 00:11:43,036
How are you so sure I'm not like them?

149
00:11:44,649 --> 00:11:47,902
All these years I just stood
by and let students die.

150
00:11:49,106 --> 00:11:50,983
I am responsible for their deaths

151
00:11:51,008 --> 00:11:52,593
just as Violet and Francisco.

152
00:11:53,024 --> 00:11:55,068
But you're not after the serum.

153
00:11:56,833 --> 00:11:58,668
You just wanted to end the lockdown

154
00:11:58,999 --> 00:12:00,292
so the killing would stop.

155
00:12:03,016 --> 00:12:04,434
So you could return to your family.

156
00:12:06,613 --> 00:12:08,407
I'm not blind, Ms. Kath.

157
00:12:08,956 --> 00:12:10,165
I'm so tired.

158
00:12:11,324 --> 00:12:13,367
I just want to set the kids free.

159
00:12:16,289 --> 00:12:17,624
I know a different way

160
00:12:18,489 --> 00:12:19,741
where Zein doesn't have to die.

161
00:12:21,051 --> 00:12:22,678
Violet and Francisco

162
00:12:23,049 --> 00:12:25,135
will pay for their fucking crimes!

163
00:12:27,986 --> 00:12:29,279
I can stop this lockdown.

164
00:12:30,006 --> 00:12:31,006
Right now.

165
00:12:31,289 --> 00:12:32,289
Tonight.

166
00:12:32,314 --> 00:12:32,898
I swear.

167
00:12:32,923 --> 00:12:34,008
Just set me free!

168
00:12:34,359 --> 00:12:35,359
But what happens

169
00:12:36,797 --> 00:12:37,797
if you fail?

170
00:12:40,291 --> 00:12:43,502
I am Supremo.

171
00:12:44,288 --> 00:12:46,123
I will not fail.

172
00:12:54,278 --> 00:12:55,278
Sorry.

173
00:12:55,875 --> 00:12:57,168
Sublevel B.

174
00:12:58,094 --> 00:12:59,971
There's an access through the service lift.

175
00:13:00,506 --> 00:13:02,252
You'll need an admin key.

176
00:13:04,914 --> 00:13:06,874
You can go through the
service tunnel. West wing.

177
00:13:08,873 --> 00:13:09,874
Good luck.

178
00:13:11,167 --> 00:13:12,210
Thank you.

179
00:13:13,044 --> 00:13:14,587
Don't thank me.

180
00:13:15,554 --> 00:13:18,178
Just do you part to finish this.

181
00:13:43,394 --> 00:13:45,104
Doc, she's almost out of blood.

182
00:13:46,299 --> 00:13:47,634
She'll die!

183
00:13:48,828 --> 00:13:50,621
We have no other choice.

184
00:13:50,646 --> 00:13:54,317
They'll kill us if we
don't extract it all tonight.

185
00:13:54,804 --> 00:13:55,804
I'm sorry, Cha.

186
00:14:16,242 --> 00:14:18,035
We don't want to take our chances.

187
00:14:18,060 --> 00:14:19,144
Harvest everything.

188
00:14:19,436 --> 00:14:21,021
Ma'am, she'll die.

189
00:14:21,643 --> 00:14:24,146
I don't care. Do it!

190
00:15:44,537 --> 00:15:45,704
Stop it!

191
00:15:47,612 --> 00:15:48,612
Traitor!

192
00:15:49,544 --> 00:15:50,833
Take her away!

193
00:15:54,729 --> 00:15:55,729
Take her.

194
00:15:58,216 --> 00:15:59,179
You!

195
00:15:59,204 --> 00:16:00,204
Assist him!

196
00:16:01,583 --> 00:16:03,168
Hurry! We're losing time.

197
00:16:05,965 --> 00:16:07,411
Resuming flow.

198
00:16:18,962 --> 00:16:19,669
Hey!

199
00:16:19,694 --> 00:16:20,694
Get down!

200
00:16:58,799 --> 00:16:59,967
Seal the door!

201
00:17:00,286 --> 00:17:01,287
Evacuate!

202
00:17:01,658 --> 00:17:02,659
Finish this now.

203
00:18:38,630 --> 00:18:39,630
He's over there!

204
00:19:25,677 --> 00:19:26,677
Darling?

205
00:19:27,277 --> 00:19:28,277
Darling.

206
00:19:28,429 --> 00:19:29,472
I'm here now.

207
00:19:30,306 --> 00:19:31,724
Darling, it's alright.

208
00:19:32,016 --> 00:19:33,142
You're safe.

209
00:19:33,143 --> 00:19:34,810
I'm here.

210
00:19:34,811 --> 00:19:35,936
Breathe.

211
00:19:35,937 --> 00:19:37,564
Okay?

212
00:19:38,966 --> 00:19:40,341
Breathe...

213
00:19:40,366 --> 00:19:41,408
One.

214
00:19:41,706 --> 00:19:42,915
Two.

215
00:19:42,940 --> 00:19:44,005
Okay.

216
00:19:44,030 --> 00:19:44,989
Inhale.

217
00:19:45,071 --> 00:19:46,071
Alright?

218
00:19:46,185 --> 00:19:47,185
You got it.

219
00:19:47,477 --> 00:19:48,477
Supremo...

220
00:19:49,659 --> 00:19:51,619
I'm sorry a little too long, okay?

221
00:19:52,287 --> 00:19:53,458
I'm sorry...

222
00:19:53,746 --> 00:19:55,290
What happened?

223
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:57,292
You came back to me.

224
00:19:57,458 --> 00:19:59,043
That's what happened.

225
00:19:59,841 --> 00:20:01,296
You said that, right?

226
00:20:02,804 --> 00:20:04,973
Don't you dare forget about it.

227
00:20:05,425 --> 00:20:07,051
Promise me you’ll never leave me alone.

228
00:20:07,385 --> 00:20:08,595
Okay?

229
00:20:10,471 --> 00:20:12,140
I can't promise anything.

230
00:20:15,059 --> 00:20:16,685
But I will stay with you

231
00:20:17,255 --> 00:20:18,688
no matter what.

232
00:20:23,192 --> 00:20:23,985
Wait

233
00:20:23,986 --> 00:20:25,820
where are my friends?

234
00:20:26,446 --> 00:20:27,447
They're safe.

235
00:20:27,739 --> 00:20:28,698
They're safe.

236
00:20:28,699 --> 00:20:30,653
You're my priority, Zein.

237
00:20:30,678 --> 00:20:31,845
Okay?

238
00:20:35,488 --> 00:20:36,739
Use this.

239
00:20:36,876 --> 00:20:37,641
Use this.

240
00:20:37,666 --> 00:20:39,231
But only if necessary.

241
00:20:39,779 --> 00:20:40,779
Okay?

242
00:20:43,004 --> 00:20:44,255
Can you run?

243
00:20:44,839 --> 00:20:45,632
I can.

244
00:20:45,632 --> 00:20:46,632
You can.

245
00:20:59,004 --> 00:21:00,255
Are you scared?

246
00:21:00,983 --> 00:21:02,234
Not anymore.

247
00:22:41,372 --> 00:22:42,415
Zein!

248
00:22:44,250 --> 00:22:45,250
Zein!

249
00:22:48,546 --> 00:22:49,546
That's enough.

250
00:23:16,727 --> 00:23:19,264
Minus aura points if you die there.

251
00:23:22,205 --> 00:23:23,206
Noted.

252
00:23:23,998 --> 00:23:24,998
Thanks.

253
00:23:25,759 --> 00:23:26,577
Next time

254
00:23:26,602 --> 00:23:27,769
I'll take the lead.

255
00:23:29,684 --> 00:23:30,685
Clear?

256
00:23:32,621 --> 00:23:33,705
Go.

257
00:23:33,841 --> 00:23:34,884
West stairs.

258
00:23:35,129 --> 00:23:36,295
Don't look back.

259
00:23:51,692 --> 00:23:52,786
Be careful.

260
00:24:09,144 --> 00:24:11,075
Who are we waiting for?

261
00:24:11,571 --> 00:24:13,106
Take it easy, my Van.

262
00:24:13,759 --> 00:24:15,135
They're coming.

263
00:24:15,733 --> 00:24:17,068
Who's coming?

264
00:24:17,234 --> 00:24:19,301
Who the fuck are we waiting for?

265
00:24:23,307 --> 00:24:24,691
I saw them earlier.

266
00:24:25,059 --> 00:24:26,685
They were taking students somewhere.

267
00:24:26,905 --> 00:24:28,700
So they could use them for an experiment?

268
00:24:29,756 --> 00:24:31,549
Something bad's going to happen to Zein.

269
00:24:31,999 --> 00:24:33,459
We have to save her.

270
00:24:33,484 --> 00:24:36,278
For sure, Zein is with Supremo.

271
00:24:36,551 --> 00:24:39,083
Can you just calm down, Ms. Savage?

272
00:24:39,108 --> 00:24:40,356
Excuse me

273
00:24:40,383 --> 00:24:42,301
don't call me that.

274
00:24:42,551 --> 00:24:44,411
We will stay here and wait.

275
00:24:44,412 --> 00:24:45,412
Wait for what?

276
00:24:45,413 --> 00:24:48,893
This is our opportunity to flee!

277
00:24:48,918 --> 00:24:49,749
What do you mean?

278
00:24:49,750 --> 00:24:51,793
Isn't Zein Shion the only one they need?

279
00:24:51,957 --> 00:24:53,025
Why should we save her?

280
00:24:53,050 --> 00:24:54,551
We're just going to get hurt!

281
00:24:56,215 --> 00:24:58,009
She's the reason why we managed to escape.

282
00:24:59,221 --> 00:25:01,723
She sacrificed herself for our freedom!

283
00:25:02,637 --> 00:25:04,161
That’s why you’re still alive.

284
00:25:04,906 --> 00:25:05,948
And now you're saying this?

285
00:25:06,229 --> 00:25:08,398
Don't you have any shame?

286
00:25:08,703 --> 00:25:10,245
Wait, stop it!

287
00:25:10,270 --> 00:25:11,688
Take it easy, bro. Calm down.

288
00:25:12,234 --> 00:25:13,651
We're all tired.

289
00:25:13,676 --> 00:25:14,760
We're all scared.

290
00:25:14,807 --> 00:25:16,661
Nothing will get solved if you guys fight.

291
00:25:18,801 --> 00:25:20,010
I like her.

292
00:25:23,701 --> 00:25:24,701
I want to go home!

293
