00:44:13,324 --> 00:44:15,410
It's over, Lux.

585
00:44:16,625 --> 00:44:19,961
This is where your fairytale ends.

586
00:44:21,504 --> 00:44:22,714
I told you

587
00:44:23,757 --> 00:44:25,675
in the real world

588
00:44:26,593 --> 00:44:28,845
it doesn't matter who's right.

589
00:44:29,512 --> 00:44:35,894
Whoever knows how to hide their stains,
they will be the one to survive.

590
00:44:37,103 --> 00:44:38,688
You won't be able to hide this.

591
00:44:39,780 --> 00:44:41,031
The world will know about this!

592
00:44:44,100 --> 00:44:45,768
You don't know what you're playing with.

593
00:44:46,396 --> 00:44:48,455
You can't control the elixir!

594
00:44:50,492 --> 00:44:51,492
You know.

595
00:44:52,410 --> 00:44:54,412
I had my doubts.

596
00:44:55,538 --> 00:44:57,582
I also told Violet about it.

597
00:45:00,361 --> 00:45:02,071
But in a perfect world

598
00:45:03,544 --> 00:45:08,090
we do crazy, sometimes
impossible things for love.

599
00:45:09,469 --> 00:45:10,469
You?

600
00:45:10,804 --> 00:45:13,681
You'll burn the world
for her, wouldn't you?

601
00:45:14,474 --> 00:45:16,935
I would do the same for Violet.

602
00:45:18,103 --> 00:45:20,605
We're both just idiots in love.

603
00:45:21,398 --> 00:45:23,149
We are not the same!

604
00:45:23,483 --> 00:45:25,902
Fuck all of you! Your time will come.

605
00:45:27,320 --> 00:45:28,320
Maybe...

606
00:45:29,345 --> 00:45:30,430
maybe not.

607
00:45:33,243 --> 00:45:35,787
But you won't be alive to find out.

608
00:45:37,038 --> 00:45:38,415
Goodbye.

609
00:45:46,714 --> 00:45:48,716
I'll see you in Hell.

610
00:46:15,201 --> 00:46:16,548
Do you remember now?

611
00:46:33,464 --> 00:46:34,841
It's been a long time

612
00:46:35,346 --> 00:46:36,681
Mr. Francisco.

613
00:46:38,230 --> 00:46:39,648
Madam Violet.

614
00:46:40,239 --> 00:46:41,949
Raze is your brother?

615
00:46:42,190 --> 00:46:43,357
Are you being serious?

616
00:46:43,792 --> 00:46:45,710
Why didn't you tell me?

617
00:46:46,624 --> 00:46:47,833
From now on,

618
00:46:48,360 --> 00:46:49,986
I'll tell you everything.

619
00:46:50,189 --> 00:46:51,482
No more secrets.

620
00:46:51,751 --> 00:46:53,169
How are you free?

621
00:46:54,324 --> 00:46:55,783
How are you alive?

622
00:46:55,808 --> 00:46:57,810
I learned from you.

623
00:46:58,215 --> 00:47:02,010
Not all your friends are true friends.

624
00:47:03,583 --> 00:47:04,709
Madam Violet

625
00:47:05,168 --> 00:47:06,836
we have you surrouned.

626
00:47:07,170 --> 00:47:08,462
Surrender now!
